title: Questions no one knows the answers to
description: TED curator Chris Anderson shares his obsession with questions that no one (yet) knows the answers to. A short intro leads into two questions: Why can't we see evidence of alien life? And how many universes are there?
author: Chris Anderson (TED)
keywords: TED, talks, TED-Ed, education, mind, science, philosophy, space, Planets, consciousness, math, physics, extraterrestrial life, curiosity, cosmos, universe, String theory, dark matter, nanoscale
